ndex=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/pleiade3/ehipp.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: An initiate enters the village</span><hr size=1> :::Hipp looks out from her window, barely being able to see past the frost that has claimed it.  She had been given word that an initiate was on her way into Themiscrya.  Hipp had readied a hut for her and had an athelfi build a fire within.  She didn't want anyone freezing on their first entrance into their new home.  Then out of the forest, she sees the huddled form moving into the village streets.  Hipp grabs her cloak and heads out quickly to meet her.<br>
As she does she walks fast and steady thru the thick snow towards the person, she can now see as the new initiate.  She waves her hands to the two archers in the trees, who had been guarding the village and were watching to see if the Queen approved of the person.  They then turned their guard back into the woods. As Hipp neared her, she did a quick amazon salute, clinking cold quantlets together:: Yasoo, athelfi.  Come....let's get you into the warmth quick. <p>@xxx}}::::::::::::::::::::>
