::She heads toward the hut with the Queen:: <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uhippolyte.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hippolyte</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://hometown.aol.com/queenhippolyte/spinningsword.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Vasilissa</span><br>  Posts: 269<br> <font color=#993300>(3/12/01 3:54:43 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=171.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/pleiade3/ehipp.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: An initiate enters the village</span><hr size=1> :::Hippolyte smiles at Ilokelesia and then looks towards a hut that they near.::: I am glad that you have made it safely to Themsicrya.  :::She steps up the steps to the hut and pushes the door open just enough for Ilokelesia to enter.::: Come, let's get in and make sure everything is to your liking. <p>@xxx}}::::::::::::::::::::>
