<br>
It is a nice hut, and I am sure I will be happy here. The journey here was long, but it appears it was worth it. My, you have such heavy snow now! I hope the winter is not too long. ::Grins and pulls up a chair to sit near the fire. She pulls a second chair up as well::<br>
